  "text": "CHO cell lines stably transfected with human FSHR have been described previously [CITATION_1] ). CHO and CHO-FSHR cell lines were maintained in Dulbecco's modified Eagle's Medium (DMEM, PAA) containing 10% fetal calf serum (FCS, Biowest), 2 mM glutamine, 100 U/mL penicillin, and 100 μg/mL streptomycin (Lonza) at 37°C in a humidified incubator gassed with 5% CO 2 .",
